<h1>Welcome to <span>Naina Beauty Parlour</span></h1>

<p>
Glow with confidence and beauty.
Professional makeup, hair styling, skincare and bridal services.
</p>

<a href="#contact" class="btn">Book Now</a>

</div>

<section id="about">

<h2 class="title">About Us</h2>

<p style="text-align:center; line-height:1.8; color:#ddd;">
Naina Beauty Parlour offers professional beauty and makeup services
with modern styling and premium care for every client.
</p>

</section>

<section id="services">

<h2 class="title">Our Services</h2>

<div class="services">

<div class="card">
<h3>Bridal Makeup</h3>
<p>Professional bridal makeup for weddings and events.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Hair Styling</h3>
<p>Modern haircuts, smoothening and styling services.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Facial & Skincare</h3>
<p>Glow treatments and skincare services.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Nail Art</h3>
<p>Creative nail extensions and nail art designs.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="gallery">

<h2 class="title">Gallery</h2>

<div class="gallery">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487412947147-5cebf100ffc2?q=80&w=1200">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512496015851-a90fb38ba796?q=80&w=1200">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522337360788-8b13dee7a37e?q=80&w=1200">

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">

<h2 class="title">Contact</h2>

<p>📍 Kolkata, India</p>
<p>📞 +91 9876543210</p>
<p>📷 Instagram: @nainabeauty</p>

<a href="#" class="btn">Call Now</a>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 Naina Beauty Parlour | All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>
